{"tid":94904,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[驚呆了]  香港天文台推出「 打 電 話 問 天 氣 加 強 版 」服務！","createTime":"2017-01-25T14:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T15:25:36.000Z","uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"efa3750f9b5e33dddf4e72371a3e9d157bd7072a","tid":94904,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:42:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/whatsnew/f2/wn20170124_uc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwhatsnew%2Ff2%2Fwn20170124_uc.htm&d=qOnrDpP%2BJXSbynmDzAHLIwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=048a10af\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/whatsnew/f2/wn20170124_uc.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/whatsnew/f2/wn20170124_fig1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwhatsnew%2Ff2%2Fwn20170124_fig1c.jpg&h=65d38b1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港天文台於今天 (2017年1月24日) 加強「打電話問天氣」服務。除了原有的天氣警告、預報、香港標準時間及地球物理資訊外，新的「打電話問天氣」服務為用戶提供更實時的分區氣溫及雨量資訊，由以往的每小時更新一次提升至分別10及15分鐘一次。同時，新服務更加入分區相對濕度及平均海平面氣壓資訊。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎市民致電1878 200使用「打電話問天氣」服務。有關服務詳情，請參閱服務指南。"},{"pid":"16d4736be84db73f5aca00456155ceaf4bc1c693","tid":94904,"uid":18044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:57:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d227e093ab27a4da7866464b1c1d6a1bd938ed","tid":94904,"uid":953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T15:11:17.000Z","msg":"記得以前細個 無聊就打18503聽又氣報告， 懷念<br />\n<br />\n依家有app 方便到差d 唔記得有依段經歷"},{"pid":"72f46e36b8de3ab7e6dcffa00ae8351d1beb1892","tid":94904,"uid":10441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25